			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="One-liner dialog for one of the Flaming Fist prison guards in the Wyrm's Rock prison that is played when the player wakes up inside the prison cell after drinking Sharess Caress' special drink. The guard talks through the bars accusing the player of carousing heavily." />
